Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.430 --> 00:00:02.710
Hoy Andrea.
Biz bu yong‘oqlarning rasmini yaratdik

00:00:02.710 --> 00:00:04.550
va bizga taqdim etgan oilaviy rasmlaringizni ham,
shuningdek,

00:00:04.550 --> 00:00:06.150
biz ularni ilovaga rasm sifatida qo‘shdik.

00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:06.689
Bu yerda uni ko‘rib chiqishingiz mumkin.

00:00:07.770 --> 00:00:09.060
&gt;&gt; Bu juda ham zo‘r.

00:00:09.060 --> 00:00:11.280
Ushbu oila a’zosi belgisiga qarang.

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:12.580
Bu xuddi buvimga o‘xshaydi.

00:00:12.580 --> 00:00:15.160
Ranglar va yong‘oqlar ham juda ajoyib.

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:17.170
Bunga qarash albatta, juda yaxshi hisni beradi.

00:00:17.170 --> 00:00:18.930
&gt;&gt; Ha, hamma narsa birgalikda
juda ajoyib ko‘rinadi.

00:00:18.930 --> 00:00:21.640
&gt;&gt; Lekin, o‘ylashimcha yana 
bir xususiyat qo‘shilishi mumkin.

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:22.490
&gt;&gt; Xo‘sh, bu nima?

00:00:22.490 --> 00:00:25.400
Bu, har bir so‘zning to‘g‘ri 
talaffuzini eshitish qobiliyati.

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:28.260
&gt;&gt; Talaffuz haqiqatdan ham
til o‘rganishda juda muhim hisoblanadi.

00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:29.650
Bu men uchun eng qiyin narsa bo‘lgan.

00:00:29.650 --> 00:00:30.200
&gt;&gt; To‘g‘ri,

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:33.760
buning uchun aytilayotgan har bir
so‘zning audio fayli kerak bo‘ladi.

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.420
Andrea, biz uchun bir nechta
audio fayllar yozib berolmaysizmi?

00:00:36.420 --> 00:00:37.370
&gt;&gt; Albatta.

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:39.040
Men talaffuzimni 
takrorlab olishim kerak.

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:40.870
&gt;&gt; Xavotir olmang.
Siz ajoyib ishni boshlamoqdasiz.

00:00:40.870 --> 00:00:45.070
Keling, o‘sha ovozli kliplarni yaratish uchun
ovoz yozish studiyasiga boraylik.

00:00:45.070 --> 00:00:47.830
&gt;&gt; Shunday qilib, keling ular buni 
qilayotganda, kurs xaritasiga qaytamiz.

00:00:47.830 --> 00:00:51.380
Hozir biz to‘rtta darsdan
to‘rtinchi darsimizdamiz.

00:00:51.380 --> 00:00:53.110
Biz hozir yakunlovchi qismdamiz.

00:00:53.110 --> 00:00:57.180
Endi ushbu darsda biz birinchi
navbatda foydalanuvchiga audio faylni, 

00:00:57.180 --> 00:00:59.425
har bir so‘z ustiga bosish orqali so‘zlarning
talaffuzini eshitishiga imkon beramiz.

